{"tid":1395274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[統計]火力應唔應該集中係星期日嘅活動","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:56:00.000Z","uid":225916,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"522ec69d538f4e8e01195239182f744ab599f3d0","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"實際上 我認為之後嘅遊行要盡量揀返星期日<br />\n因為星期六始終有一班人仲要返工 包括我在內<br />\n唔係個個星期六都可以全日出席到<br />\n所以想統計一下<br />\n到底有幾多人 星期六係比較難準時出戰<br />\n<br />\n可以準時/冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會遲到/未必去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設結果出嚟 佔嘅比率唔少<br />\n大家應該考慮將火力集中於星期日嘅活動<br />\n而唔係星期六<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e912308029fcff2a86ad2d239cc08feab1609b5b","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a98734046bc3d71a1e971523c19a53c5521fe217","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad167a4ebbbed64e5e3f34cdae50f3d91b805f2","tid":1395274,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span>"},{"pid":"68fdc5b8632c6a6cb230c7cc28d211aebb2e2b96","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:45:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d181107fdb65f4be6e5caa40d9859a7d7a2fe41f","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9f61ee422754de232792a27a19868ebb3f2cdf8","tid":1395274,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited